devdoc.details: A simple FIFO queue for unsigned integers.

dequeue().details: Dequeues the first uint256 value from the queue.

enqueue(uint256).details: Enqueues a uint256 value into the queue.

isEmpty().details: Checks whether the queue is empty.

peek().details: Peeks at the first uint256 value without removing it.

size().details: Returns the current size of the queue.

returns._0: The number of elements in the queue.

@title FIFOQueueUint
 @dev A simple FIFO queue for unsigned integers.

@dev Enqueues a uint256 value into the queue.
 @param item The value to enqueue.
